title: Intervals - In Time EP (Official Guitar Transcription)
description:
Description:

"The Complete Guitar Transcription for Intervals' 2012 album "In Time".

Toronto's Intervals are anything but ordinary. They write complex yet groovy instrumental songs that actually feel like songs.

Each track telling a story - even if some are at incredibly fast speeds.
5 songs sounds like your average EP, but these guys cram two album's worth of notes and expression in there!

If you need to work on any aspect of your playing, Aaron and Lukas have probably already done some of the work for you.

Enjoy this paperless transcription of their incredible EP "In Time" and why not crank their tunes? A download of the entire album comes with it for free after all!

*this is a high resolution digital guitar book. an immediate link will be provided to you upon purchase. Make sure you check your junk mail folder if you don't see it!

Tunings:
Ab Eb Ab Db Gb Bb Eb - Alchemy, Mata Hari, Tapestry, Epiphany
C G C F A D - Momento
"



Notices:

1. This download includes ONLY the official Guitar Pro files. You'll need Guitar Pro 6 or a newer version to open the .gpx files.
2. PLEASE SEED! Other people may want this content as bad as you, so make sure to seed at least at 1:1.
3. Make sure to support the musicians you love by buying their content if you can!
